description:
BIMM London were lucky enough to be joined by legendary drummer Steve Jordan. With such an incredible career in the industry, it was great to have him here to talk drum technique and give some one-on-one drum advice. 

Subscribe to BIMM on YouTube: http://bit.ly/1mf8nTm

BIMM, The British and Irish Modern Music Institute, has colleges in eight cities where music matters most – London, Berlin, Dublin, Manchester, Bristol, Birmingham ,Hamburg, and Brighton – and is proud to be the largest and leading provider of contemporary music education in the UK, Ireland and Europe.
Find out more: http://ow.ly/PoGl307iins
title: Steve Jordan talks Drum Technique - BIMM Masterclass
